						<summary>

						<p>This is of the same date and reign as No. 584 above. It enumerates the various buildings and shrines erected in the temple of Mahālakshmīdēvi at <hi rend="bold">Haruhe-Lakkhaṇāpura</hi> by the brothers <hi rend="bold">Virapaṇṇa</hi> and <hi rend="bold">Vīraṇa-Nāyaka</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Penugoṇḍe.</hi> </p>						

